<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currently, Zend_Amf_Adobe_Auth will load ACLs from a given file. In order to use those ACLs with the server, you must do the following:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$auth = new Zend_Amf_Adobe_Auth($xmlAclFile);
$server-&gt;setAuth($auth)
       -&gt;setAcl($auth-&gt;getAcl());
</code></pre>

<p>Ideally, calling setAuth() with an object that implements a getAcl() method should auto-invoke setAcl() with the return value of getAcl().</p>

